"use strict";(self.webpackChunkvnanikalyan_github_io=self.webpackChunkvnanikalyan_github_io||[]).push([[1375],{441:function(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"random-writings","metadata":{"permalink":"/fr/blog/random-writings","editUrl":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io/blog/blog/random-writings.md","source":"@site/blog/random-writings.md","title":"Random Writings","description":"We are inventing new stuff so that we will have more time?","date":"2021-12-11T15:28:19.623Z","formattedDate":"11 d\xe9cembre 2021","tags":[{"label":"Wisdom","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/wisdom"},{"label":"Random","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/random"},{"label":"Philosophy","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/philosophy"}],"readingTime":0.89,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"Nani Kalyan","title":"Senior Software Engineer @ MNC","url":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16670359?v=4","key":"vnk"}],"nextItem":{"title":"John Piper on Ravi Zacharias","permalink":"/fr/blog/john-piper-on-rz"}},"content":"We are inventing new stuff so that we will have more time?\\n\\nWhat we will do with more time? Again invent? Or Rich becoming richer.\\n\\nWhat\'s the point of invention? To understand the world better and use the things that are there in the nature\\n- Waves\\n- Light etc\\n\\nAnyways we are all gonna die one day or the other then what\'s the point of invention? To become inter-planetary species?\\n\\nEven on another planet, we will die for sure. What if we came for a cure for death. Living forever and storing a humongous amount of data in our brain. what is the point of living forever.\\n\\nTo enjoy pleasures. All pleasures will eventually lose pleasure, particularly for an individual.\\n\\nThen what\'s the point of \\n\\t1) Invention \\n\\t2) Living forever \\n\\t3) Having More time...\\n\\nDo What you like? Is that the solution?\\nIf everybody wants to do what they like then there would be chaos.\\nWe invent to avoid chaos and bring order.\\n\\nThere is order all around us in Nature. Planetary motions, light speed, seasons, etc."},{"id":"john-piper-on-rz","metadata":{"permalink":"/fr/blog/john-piper-on-rz","editUrl":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io/blog/blog/Theology/john-piper-on-rz.mdx","source":"@site/blog/Theology/john-piper-on-rz.mdx","title":"John Piper on Ravi Zacharias","description":"John Piper on Ravi Zacharias","date":"2021-12-11T15:28:19.623Z","formattedDate":"11 d\xe9cembre 2021","tags":[],"readingTime":0.335,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"Nani Kalyan","title":"Senior Software Engineer @ MNC","url":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16670359?v=4","key":"vnk"}],"prevItem":{"title":"Random Writings","permalink":"/fr/blog/random-writings"},"nextItem":{"title":"Next Generation Leader","permalink":"/fr/blog/nextgen-leader-andy-stanley"}},"content":"John Piper on Ravi Zacharias\\n\\nThis age through religious work\\n\\t1) Association with notable people\\n\\t2) Access to money\\n\\t3) Experiences of power\\n\\t4) Accolades for eloquence\\n\\t5) commendations for courage\\nplenty of wordly pleasures\\n\\nHymenias\\n1 Timohty 1:20\\nDid not hold faith in Good Conscience\\n\\n1) \\n2) Forsaking a Good Conscince prelude to moral disaster\\n3) The Amassing of Money and pursuit of lavish life style"},{"id":"nextgen-leader-andy-stanley","metadata":{"permalink":"/fr/blog/nextgen-leader-andy-stanley","editUrl":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io/blog/blog/Theology/nextgen-leader-andy-stanley.md","source":"@site/blog/Theology/nextgen-leader-andy-stanley.md","title":"Next Generation Leader","description":"Next Generation Leader: Andy Stanley","date":"2021-12-11T15:28:19.623Z","formattedDate":"11 d\xe9cembre 2021","tags":[{"label":"Leader","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/leader"}],"readingTime":0.385,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"Nani Kalyan","title":"Senior Software Engineer @ MNC","url":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16670359?v=4","key":"vnk"}],"prevItem":{"title":"John Piper on Ravi Zacharias","permalink":"/fr/blog/john-piper-on-rz"},"nextItem":{"title":"Money","permalink":"/fr/blog/view-on-money"}},"content":"Next Generation Leader: Andy Stanley\\n\\nHe mentions **5 Characteristics** of a Leader in his book  \\n1) **_The less you do the more you accomplish_**  \\n2) **_The less you do you will let others to accomplish_**\\n\\nThe rise of a Chaotic Age - *D Hawk*  \\nWe all lead from 4 different levels  \\n- We lead ourselves       (50%)  \\n- We lead those above us  (25%)  \\n- we lead those around us (12.5%)  \\n- We lead those below us  (12.5%)"},{"id":"view-on-money","metadata":{"permalink":"/fr/blog/view-on-money","editUrl":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io/blog/blog/Theology/view-on-money.md","source":"@site/blog/Theology/view-on-money.md","title":"Money","description":"Prosperity Consciousness Vs Poverty consciousness.","date":"2021-12-11T15:28:19.623Z","formattedDate":"11 d\xe9cembre 2021","tags":[{"label":"Money","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/money"}],"readingTime":0.92,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"Nani Kalyan","title":"Senior Software Engineer @ MNC","url":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16670359?v=4","key":"vnk"}],"prevItem":{"title":"Next Generation Leader","permalink":"/fr/blog/nextgen-leader-andy-stanley"},"nextItem":{"title":"Wise words by Kunal Shah","permalink":"/fr/blog/kunal-shah-wise-words"}},"content":"Prosperity Consciousness Vs Poverty consciousness.  \\n\\nMoney is a Good Servant but a Bad Master.\\n\\n**George Bernard Shaw**  \\n- It is the duty of every person to be rich  \\n- It is a sin to be poor\\n\\nNatural Laws (Divine Laws)  \\n1) ***Everything moves***  \\n- Moving forward or backward  \\n- Grow or Die  \\n- Becoming richer or poorer\\n\\n2) ***Sowing and Reaping***  \\n- Thoughts,  \\n- emotions,  \\n- feelings \\nare the seeds that you sow...Harvest you reap \\nCause and Effect\\n\\nSin & Money  \\n- Breaking the law. Penality is Death. (you are going back)\\n\\t\\t- you are tyring to reap without sowing\\n\\t\\t- Getting without giving\\n\\tMoney - is the reward you receive when you render a service. Higher the valuable to service higher the reward.\\n\\t\\t\\t- Getting money without rendering service is SIN.\\n\\tIf a person receives money in an unlawful manner they will pay the price just wait.\\n\\nMatthew - Biblical proof\\n\\nfg+e=I\\n\\nFG = financial Goals\\ne = expenses\\nI = Income\\n\\nFinancial Goals\\n\\t- Two Things\\n\\t\\t i) People working for Money\\n\\t\\tii) Money working for Money\\nMSI - Multiple sources of Income"},{"id":"kunal-shah-wise-words","metadata":{"permalink":"/fr/blog/kunal-shah-wise-words","editUrl":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io/blog/blog/2021-12-11-kunalshah.md","source":"@site/blog/2021-12-11-kunalshah.md","title":"Wise words by Kunal Shah","description":"Money","date":"2021-12-11T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"11 d\xe9cembre 2021","tags":[{"label":"Wisdom","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/wisdom"},{"label":"kunal shah","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/kunal-shah"},{"label":"cred","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/cred"},{"label":"freecharge","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/freecharge"}],"readingTime":0.885,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"Nani Kalyan","title":"Senior Software Engineer @ MNC","url":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16670359?v=4","key":"vnk"}],"prevItem":{"title":"Money","permalink":"/fr/blog/view-on-money"},"nextItem":{"title":"Social Media Facts","permalink":"/fr/blog/social-media-facts"}},"content":"**Money** \\n    It is a method to unlock choices in life.\\n\\n**Ambition**\\n    To find a purpose to live\\n\\n**self-awareness**\\n    There is real us and what we think of us.\\n    Merging these two is self-awareness\\n\\nThe curse of Fame\\nChase skill, knowledge, understanding instead of Fame\\n\\nCan there be 4000 Javeline winners? No.\\nCan there be 5 million millionaires this month? Yes.\\n\\nZeroSum\\nZeroSome\\n\\nUnderstand Human Behaviour. \\n\\nHuman Motivation is constantly changing.\\n\\nEverybody has different amounts of money to spend but same amount of time to spend.\\nonly 24 hours.\\n\\n2 transactions\\n\\t- Boring Transactions\\n\\t\\t- Pumping petrol\\n\\t\\t- If there are two bunks and one offers two ruppees cheap then They will go that pump but in case of shoes the vice-versa.\\n\\t- Interesting Transactions\\n\\t\\t- Coz purchasing and wearing shoes is interesting\\n\\n* We became better humans by incentive system.\\nGood Behaviour - good incentive\\nBad Behaviour - Punishment\\n\\n\\nAlternative ways of getting Validation\\n\\t- A rude kid who solved the water carrying problem (Invented bucket)\\n\\t- He became rich and everybody started talking good about him"},{"id":"social-media-facts","metadata":{"permalink":"/fr/blog/social-media-facts","editUrl":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io/blog/blog/2021-12-11-life-facts.md","source":"@site/blog/2021-12-11-life-facts.md","title":"Social Media Facts","description":"Highlight Reel","date":"2021-12-11T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"11 d\xe9cembre 2021","tags":[{"label":"Wisdom","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/wisdom"},{"label":"facts","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/facts"},{"label":"life","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/life"}],"readingTime":0.21,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"Nani Kalyan","title":"Senior Software Engineer @ MNC","url":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16670359?v=4","key":"vnk"}],"prevItem":{"title":"Wise words by Kunal Shah","permalink":"/fr/blog/kunal-shah-wise-words"},"nextItem":{"title":"welcome","permalink":"/fr/blog/welcome"}},"content":"Highlight Reel\\nSocial Currency\\nFear of Missing Out\\nOnline Harrasement\\n\\nStronger Economy means\\t\\n\\t- Eating more Fat and Sugar\\n\\t- Moving Less\\n\\t- Breathing lot more air pollution\\n\\t- Living Longer\\n- All the above factors increase the likely hood of Stroke"},{"id":"welcome","metadata":{"permalink":"/fr/blog/welcome","editUrl":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io/blog/blog/2021-12-11-welcome/index.md","source":"@site/blog/2021-12-11-welcome/index.md","title":"welcome","description":"The content on this website is my learnings as a freelancer, software developer to senior software developer. I used to write my learnings on documents.","date":"2021-12-11T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"11 d\xe9cembre 2021","tags":[{"label":"welcome","permalink":"/fr/blog/tags/welcome"}],"readingTime":0.26,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"Nani Kalyan","title":"Senior Software Engineer @ MNC","url":"https://vnanikalyan.github.io","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16670359?v=4","key":"vnk"}],"prevItem":{"title":"Social Media Facts","permalink":"/fr/blog/social-media-facts"}},"content":"The content on this website is my learnings as a freelancer, software developer to senior software developer. I used to write my learnings on documents.\\n\\nTo refer them has become cumbersome. Thought of putting all of them on website so that referring would be easy and might help other developers out there."}]}')}}]);